Petrobras Interested in BG Stakes in Brazil, Economico Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-10-14T12:03:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/petrobras-interested-in-bg-stakes-in-brazil-economico-says.html
Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4)  would
exercise the right of first refusal in the event that  BG Group
Plc (BG/)  sold stakes in its Brazilian oil fields, Brasil Economico
reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Jose Sergio Gabrielli.  Petrobras, as the state-controlled oil company is known,
hasn’t been informed by BG that it’s interested in selling
assets in Brazil, he told the Sao Paulo-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts  at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  